content.text: is designed to provide a comprehensive pivoted summary of fiscal year billing and usage data by agency, facility, and account. It aggregates and pivots monthly billing and usage data into fiscal year-to-date summaries, allowing for comparative analysis of original and revised billing amounts, energy usage, and demand. The view is constructed using a combination of subqueries, aggregations, and multiple PIVOT operations to transform detailed transactional data into a format suitable for reporting and analysis.
The complexity of this view is high due to several factors:
: The view employs numerous PIVOT operations to transform monthly data into a fiscal year format, which adds complexity to the SQL logic.
: Subqueries are used to dynamically fetch the current and prior fiscal years, as well as the current billing period, adding to the complexity.
